Description: Multifidelity optimization methods based on the successive
    halving algorithm. Implements the successive halving, asynchronous
    successive halving, hyperband and asynchronous hyperband algorithm as
    general purpose optimizers for 'bbotk' and tuners for `mlr3tuning`. Various
    termination criteria can be set and combined. If possible learners are
    hotstarted to accelerate tuning. The class 'AutoTuner' provides a convenient
    way to perform nested resampling in combination with 'mlr3'.
